About the report

  • This is a free report and authors do not admit any responsibility about the report or the data.
  • This report is meant to refresh itself each day automatically. Essentially an R package, an external python script and Github Actions make it possible. Blog post to follow soon…
  • Data is taken from EPIAS Seffaflik Platformu, data provider of the Turkish Energy Exchange.
  • Almost all code is openly shared on its Github repository. You may use the code in line with the license (MIT license).
  • For improvement, analysis and data requests contact me on Linkedin. For raw data csv files click here.
